		description: ["Every weapon is a hollow thing until the godess Kieransmama breathes life into it. Use the scroll on the spear. Then apply the Socket Orb to unlock its true potential.", "This is the Mine & Slash soul — the stat-building layer. There is also a Soul Land Martial Soul running a parallel cultivation track. Both are worth your time. Both feed the same endgame. See Side D."]
