		description: ["You have chosen the Plate Path. Your iron armor will become heavy plate — built to absorb punishment and hold the line. Use each of the three Force Soul Tag: Armor modifiers on your Chestplate, Leggings, and Boots to lock in the plate archetype across the full set. Do not complete the other paths."]
